[51 Disciple] Chem (Iksar) [The Silent Majority]<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yizanpetpimpin>Yizan Pet Pimpin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#333333>(11/26/02 8:03:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7981.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home1.gte.net/res0rg9w/tomoanim3.gif width=100 height=125></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Magician for me?</span><hr size=1> Since PoP I have noticed a GREAT increase in peoples perception of me as a mage.  I used to LFG for a while then go solo if I had to, now I get tells from people in other zones if I have my LFG flag up while shopping / banking in PoK, mages must be doing some thing right! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
